{"tid":1111881,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"畸寶你報新聞抽水抽到咁點X得","createTime":"2019-04-17T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T04:58:38.000Z","uid":35365,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"601e65ed9c6705925d8ac4b601e36723ecf0e28b","tid":1111881,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"歐聯八強次回合，巴塞羅那有美斯攻入兩球及古天奴的世界波，主場大勝曼聯三比零，兩回合計淨勝四球。 <br />\n<br />\n巴塞首回合只是贏一比零，回到主場未能<span style=\"color: red;\">安心</span>，曼聯的拉舒福特偷到位，三十多秒，一推一射中橫楣，曼聯禁區有接觸，費特落腳，拉傑迪跌低了，球證堅定直指十二碼，<span style=\"color: red;\">鏡頭無處不在，真相無所遁形</span>，球證去場邊看過重播，決定改變主意，沒有十二碼。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼聯在十六強次回合絕地反擊淘汰聖日耳門，機會<span style=\"color: red;\">只怕沒那麼多</span>，拉舒福特有點腳滑，未能把握，艾殊利楊格一扣再解圍被截到，飛剷補救都差半步，落在美斯腳下，推大位起腳，十六分鐘巴塞開紀錄，<span style=\"color: red;\">惟獨美斯不可取替</span>，一次機會就為巴塞入球，連一向令人心安的迪基亞都犯了天下門將都會犯的錯，美斯射門竟然漏入了，二十分鐘連入兩球，<span style=\"color: red;\">很丟臉、很陌生的迪基亞</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">做錯一刻或者沒有了靈魂，給時間他找回自己吧</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">雨後陽光</span>，迪基亞上半場補時救走必入球，封走沙治奧羅拔圖射空門，移位夠快，近距離硬接一招，曼聯今屆歐聯只好煞科。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換邊後，<span style=\"color: red;\">古天奴發熱發亮拉出世界波，弧線這樣難捉摸</span>，在迪基亞手頂過，六十一分鐘，三比零，總比數贏到四球，曼聯還好嗎？還有美斯倒掛柱邊出底線，<span style=\"color: red;\">總算沒那麼傷</span>，達洛特傳中山齊士頭槌，達史迪根救到，紅魔鬼曼聯未能破蛋，美斯補時階段過不到迪基亞，巴塞結果淨勝三球，兩回合計贏四比零降魔，<span style=\"color: red;\">安心準備四強</span>，鬥利物浦跟波圖的勝方。<br />\n<br />\ncls 記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d601e95f25f82d1ce900fffa607a8445b355486","tid":1111881,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"加返條link<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/546886/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%AD%90%E8%81%AF%E5%85%AB%E5%BC%B7%E6%AC%A1%E5%9B%9E%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E7%BE%85%E9%82%A33%EF%BC%9A0%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F546886%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A1%259E%25E7%25BE%2585%25E9%2582%25A33%25EF%25BC%259A0%25E6%259B%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=7f60ba0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F546886%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A1%259E%25E7%25BE%2585%25E9%2582%25A33%25EF%25BC%259A0%25E6%259B%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF&h=30952891\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/546886/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%AD%90%E8%81%AF%E5%85%AB%E5%BC%B7%E6%AC%A1%E5%9B%9E%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E7%BE%85%E9%82%A33%EF%BC%9A0%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF</a>"},{"pid":"98660cf1cf46ba7547b2e2168f8b9361afe15ca1","tid":1111881,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc8d7abdadda06bd69b3f852fa818f5f1a6c87d","tid":1111881,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src