.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"漏左<span style=\"color: red;\">煞科</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今朝睇畸寶早晨笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa92a2041fc68376251ec777cddee36099031e3","tid":1111881,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:21:39.000Z","msg":"迪基亞係一個壞左既keeper"},{"pid":"56dddde0f4350edc2e29a02287b1358e388446f2","tid":1111881,"uid":191974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"降魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92263a65dbebeefdf15d516355ca231c777346d","tid":1111881,"uid":70505,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"犯了天下門將都會犯的錯"},{"pid":"8354488f343dc6338bacc6d7ef4a4f010d5aa312","tid":1111881,"uid":35587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"降魔"},{"pid":"7757f60d6e5e028534e153481cca35cb79c70393","tid":1111881,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"痴線 報新聞加落去又岩 我係上司實升佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0707aac9859d8f7fdfca23e116da81279c9e98","tid":1111881,"uid":231674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"降魔的巴塞"},{"pid":"af2e006b5622ce0d68330e6ce750366aa70dcf34","tid":1111881,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72a80ad33d79dc2811eb0e020e4fdd587285b81","tid":1111881,"uid":165817,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:35:45.000Z","msg":"其實真係體現到，伍晃榮對體育新聞報導有幾大影響力<br />\n<br />\n以前體育報導都係好死板，係伍生改變咗成個風格，將啲近期發生嘅事用諷刺手法溝入故仔，再用幽默手法帶出嚟，跟住佢徒弟伍家謙都算承傳到呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n之後到大文豪水杯事件、安心出軌呢啲娛樂新聞，都撈埋入去抽水。而家睇好似好常態咁，但伍晃榮呢下真係創新兼影響深遠"},{"pid":"505063a40f897829f85675e1d7de8caee50fe04f","tid":1111881,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:16:06.000Z","msg":"成篇都語帶相關 <br />\ncls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be68822f01042a7d0cdef3ef501d74eb722b846","tid":1111881,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:25:55.000Z","msg":"呢度係internet，你可以爆粗"},{"pid":"76647f7b3369be635deafe7569cf3ae668603417","tid":1111881,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be68822f01042a7d0cdef3ef501d74eb722b846","tid":1111881,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:25:55.000Z","msg":"呢度係internet，你可以爆粗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:29:44.000Z","msg":"alan唔畀"},{"pid":"73f447bdb3b1585acd1c9a4d6e9dd1bf93e7166e","tid":1111881,"uid":117422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2049c88fabeedcd7422c652e9aed6f039207c87","tid":1111881,"uid":81054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e862f7e9722a30c78114c0d357713fe20454220","tid":1111881,"uid":59869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"601e65ed9c6705925d8ac4b601e36723ecf0e28b","tid":1111881,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"歐聯八強次回合，巴塞羅那有美斯攻入兩球及古天奴的世界波，主場大勝曼聯三比零，兩回合計淨勝四球。 <br />\n<br />\n巴塞首回合只是贏一比零，回到主場未能<span style=\"color: red;\">安心</span>，曼聯的拉舒福特偷到位，三十多秒，一推一射中橫楣，曼聯禁區有接觸，費特落腳，拉傑迪跌低了，球證堅定直指十二碼，<span style=\"color: red;\">鏡頭無處不在，真相無所遁形</span>，球證去場邊看過重播，決定改變主意，沒有十二碼。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼聯在十六強次回合絕地反擊淘汰聖日耳門，機會<span style=\"color: red;\">只怕沒那麼多</span>，拉舒福特有點腳滑，未能把握，艾殊利楊格一扣再解圍被截到，飛剷補救都差半步，落在美斯腳下，推大位起腳，十六分鐘巴塞開紀錄，<span style=\"color: red;\">惟獨美斯不可取替</span>，一次機會就為巴塞入球，連一向令人心安的迪基亞都犯了天下門將都會犯的錯，美斯射門竟然漏入了，二十分鐘連入兩球，<span style=\"color: red;\">很丟臉、很陌生的迪基亞</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">做錯一刻或者沒有了靈魂，給時間他找回自己吧</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">雨後陽光</span>，迪基亞上半場補時救走必入球，封走沙治奧羅拔圖射空門，移位夠快，近距離硬接一招，曼聯今屆歐聯只好煞科。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換邊後，<span style=\"color: red;\">古天奴發熱發亮拉出世界波，弧線這樣難捉摸</span>，在迪基亞手頂過，六十一分鐘，三比零，總比數贏到四球，曼聯還好嗎？還有美斯倒掛柱邊出底線，<span style=\"color: red;\">總算沒那麼傷</span>，達洛特傳中山齊士頭槌，達史迪根救到，紅魔鬼曼聯未能破蛋，美斯補時階段過不到迪基亞，巴塞結果淨勝三球，兩回合計贏四比零降魔，<span style=\"color: red;\">安心準備四強</span>，鬥利物浦跟波圖的勝方。<br />\n<br />\ncls 記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"漏左<span style=\"color: red;\">煞科</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今朝睇畸寶早晨笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"仲有「還好嗎？」"}]}